Use story:
As a user of the datasore I want to be able to put the resource id without the dataset name in a url and see the resource page.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Proposed redirect:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
/resource/{res-id} -&amp;gt; dataset/foo-bar/resource/{res-id}
&lt;/p&gt;
